FBIS4-21959 "jptot015__l94124" JPRS-TOT-94-015-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 2 April 1994 WEST EUROPE TURKEY Arrest of Six PKK Members Includes DEP District Official Arrest of Six PKK Members Includes DEP District Official TA0204083194 Ankara Turkiye Radyolari Network in Turkish 0430 GMT 2 Apr 94 TA0204083194 Ankara Turkiye Radyolari Network Turkish BFN [Text] Six members of the PKK [Workers Party of Kurdistan], including a woman, have been arrested in Elbistan District in Kahramanmaras. One of the suspects is the head Democracy Party official for Elbistan. Our correspondent has learned that two of the suspects were involved in various terrorist activities in the area. The other four abetted the organization.
